      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Frontier Developer Cockpit is the local developer cockpit for GitHub Copilot and agentic development telemetry. Use it to learn from real local sessions, improve prompt shape, reduce context waste, understand model labels, inspect tool behavior, and validate local data quality. For live GenAI traces, use Aspire. For centralized enterprise history, use Frontier FinOps Cockpit in Azure."
      }
    },
